high_descs: turn around, walk to the other side of the toilet
take the plunger on the ground
turn left to the cabinet
open the right cabinet door, put the plunger in, close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: move the plunger from the side of the toilet to the cabinet

high_descs: turn to the right and go forward past the toilet and turn to the right
pick up the plunger left of the toilet
turn to the left facing the cabinet
open the right hand side of the cabinet and place the plunger in it and close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a plunger in the cabinet near the toilet

high_descs: Turn right, move past the toilet, turn right and move to the toilet paper.
Pick up the plunger on the ground.
Turn left and bring the plunger to the lower right cabinet.
Put the plunger in the lower right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the plunger in the lower right cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and go to stand to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the plunger from the floor.
Turn to the left and face the cabinet on the far right.
Put the plunger in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the plunger in the far right cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the sink, turn right then walk towards the roll of toilet paper on the wall.
Pick up the red plunger near the toilet.
Turn left towards the sink.
Open the cabinet on the right side underneath the sink then place the plunger behind the box of tissue.
anns.task_desc: Place a red plunger underneath a sink located closest to the wall.
